1.8
log
@convert to new .Dd format;
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: quotaon.8,v 1.7 2007/02/18 23:04:56 jmc Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 1983, 1990, 1991, 1993
.\"	The Regents of the University of California.  All rights reserved.
